    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（今日は星見市で野外フェスが開催される日だ）\n（サニーピースもステージでパフォーマンスを披露した）",
      "startTime": 3.8539653102556866,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫か、怜\nいつもより、息が上がっているみたいだけど",
      "startTime": 8.864447714732243,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……はぁ……大丈夫です……\nちょっと気合が入り過ぎただけですから",
      "startTime": 16.470827529206872,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それなんだが……今日の怜のダンス\nいつもと比べてぎこちない気がしたんだ",
      "startTime": 23.133333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "……っ\n私は、いつも通り踊ったつもりです",
      "startTime": 26.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "具体的に、どこがぎこちなく感じたんですか？",
      "startTime": 29.49625835418703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "普段より、動きも表情も硬かったと思う\n気のせいか？",
      "startTime": 36.4138659000397,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "…………そう、ですか\nやっぱり……そう見えちゃってたんですね",
      "startTime": 41.15929670333865,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}さんの言う通りです\nホントはちょっと……調子が出ませんでした",
      "startTime": 47.410229461257536,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "よりにもよって今日\nこんなふがいないダンスを……",
      "startTime": 52.4732934848122,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "いや、そこまでは言ってない\nいつも通り高いレベルでまとまってはいたけど",
      "startTime": 57.03904445872588,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "……ありがとうございます\nでも、それじゃあダメなんです",
      "startTime": 62.69245718809274,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "誰が見ても文句が出ないぐらいの\n圧倒的なパフォーマンスを披露しないと……っ",
      "startTime": 67.79836684862772,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "怜……分かった\nでもまずは、楽屋に戻って少しクールダウンしよう",
      "startTime": 73.74120837226508,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8021.1101705332485,
          "startTime": 81.76231854279833
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "……すみません",
      "startTime": 77.43032307624814,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（……怜の様子がおかしい）\n（いったいどうしたんだ？）",
      "startTime": 81.97565187613166,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "danceb",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチB",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-danceb001.m4a",
      "text": "……あの、すみません。怜のマネージャーさんですよね\n実は私、怜の……",
      "startTime": 89.88170576964811,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "怜、ここにいたんだな\nそろそろ帰り支度しようか",
      "startTime": 96.80898520946504,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……\nすみません、考え事をしてて。すぐ着替えてきます",
      "startTime": 100.90898520946504,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "今日、怜が通っていたダンススクールの先生が\n見に来てたんだな",
      "startTime": 108.59428841778734,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "――えっ！？\n{user}さん、なんでそれ……",
      "startTime": 111.15449322406045,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "さっき、挨拶に来て下さったんだよ",
      "startTime": 113.95127320341946,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "そういうことでしたか……",
      "startTime": 116.43780386500241,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "……ステージの上って、ライトが明る過ぎて\n意外と客席って見えてないんですよ",
      "startTime": 122.23780386500243,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "でも……先生だけはすぐ、いるのが分かりました\nこっちを――私を見てるって、気付いたんです",
      "startTime": 130.110487114582,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、結構目力の強い人だったからな\n見られてたら感じ取れるか",
      "startTime": 139.4426908735186,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-rei015.m4a",
      "text": "それもありますけど……単純に\n他のお客さんと違って微動だにしてなかったから",
      "startTime": 144.3636811950174,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-rei016.m4a",
      "text": "それで、先生がこっちを見てるって\n分かった時、私……思わず、体がこわばっちゃって",
      "startTime": 152.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "それって、先生のことが怖いから……とか？",
      "startTime": 158.12906172590445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-rei017.m4a",
      "text": "い、いえ、違いますよ\n大体なんですか、その子供みたいな理由",
      "startTime": 165.2681772819857,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-rei018.m4a",
      "text": "確かに先生は厳しい人ですけど\n同じぐらい優しい人なんですから",
      "startTime": 171.54890628289448,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
